          Careers        





















Now Seeking Forward Thinkers
Join Leidos to help make our communities, our nation, and our world a better place for generations to come.





Submit



Submitted a resume? Access your existing profile »
Are you a Leidos employee? Access your employee profile here »
Having Technical Issues Applying to a Position?If you are having technical issues applying to a position on leidos.com/careers, we’d be happy to assist. Request help now »
Accommodation Request - If you have a disability and need help using leidos.com/careers, we'd be happy to lend a hand. Request help now »
Leidos will never send funds to employees except for regular salary payments upon becoming an employee of the company. In addition, Leidos will never ask potential candidates to provide payment-related information or remit payments to others during the hiring process. Leidos will only communicate with potential candidates through company emails that contain the Leidos domain; @leidos.com, which are generated by our automated system. Leidos never conducts job interviews through online methods such as Google Hangouts or other chat functions. If you receive an email claiming to be from Leidos with either of the above examples to include asking for other personal identifiable information (PII), please report the email, any associated job sites and job listings to Chris Scalia, VP of Talent Acquisition, at chris.a.scalia@leidos.com.





