Life at Leidos
View All »




Balance Work & Life

At Leidos, we offer meaningful and engaging careers, a collaborative culture, and support for your career goals, all while nurturing a healthy work-life balance.
Learn More »



Build Your Career

Grow with us. We offer resources for professional development and learning, complemented by flexible career paths and an inclusive environment.
Learn More »




Our Values
View All »






INTEGRITY
Integrity is having the courage to make the tough calls, taking pride in our work, being transparent with our team, and being respectful of everyone.






INNOVATION
Innovation is not limited to our engineers and scientists. We must all act as catalysts. Be tenacious and curious to help us excel, and be a part of a learning organization.






AGILITY
Agility is our ability to think and act small while using the size and strength of our balance sheet to our advantage. It is about being flexible, creative, and resilient.






COLLABORATION
Collaboration is being inclusive, team-oriented, and proactively engaging—building relationships and staying connected with each other.






COMMITMENT
Commitment to our customers and our team means we are accountable, take ownership, model servant leadership, and operate with a sense of urgency.






Pay & Benefits
View All »




Compensation

We reward your contributions to the company and our customers' mission, recognizing notable advances in your field. 
Learn More »



Health Coverage

Benefits start immediately, with no waiting period, no exclusions for pre-existing conditions, and comprehensive coverage for employees and their eligible dependents.
Learn More »



Wellness

Certain locations provide full-service fitness centers which offer cardio and strength training equipment, as well as group exercise classes.
Learn More »




Careers FAQs
View All »



What is the status of my application?
Log into your Candidate Profile and go to the "My Job" page. You'll be able to see your application's current status and whether the position you applied for is still open.


Where can I find benefits information?
You'll find general information about our compensation packages in the Pay & Benefits section. You'll get more specifics when extended a job offer.


How do I send an updated resume?
To update a job submission, go to the "My Job" page, find the submission you want to update, click "View/Edit Submission", make your edits, and submit changes.


How will I know if you've received my resume?
You'll get an automatic email confirmation as soon as you register and submit your resume via this site.


















 
 




