If you are a Leidos Employee
All updates for current Leidos employees can be made through Workday. View the Workday community on Prism so you're aware of browser requirements and can find helpful quick reference guides.
If you are a former Leidos Employee
Former employees can update their address by contacting the Shared Services Center at 1-855-553-4367 or complete the Former Employee Address Change form and submit directly to HR via fax, mail, or email (full instructions are provided in pdf).



How to Obtain Verification of Current or Former* Employment
Current and former* Leidos (formerly known as SAIC) employees can provide proof of employment and income with secure, 24/7 access through a toll-free number and website.
Here is the process for current Leidos and former* SAIC employees (*employment prior to 9/28/2013), outside firms, or agencies requesting verification:

Current and *Former Employees Initiating Verification
If you are an employee initiating verification, supply the firm or agency with the following:

Your Social Security number
Leidos (formerly SAIC) employer code: 12275
One-time use salary key (only needed for income verification). To establish a salary key, call 800-367-2884 or go to The Work Number® and select the "Enter Employee Section" link.

Note: If you left Leidos (formerly SAIC) prior to 9/28/2013, please use the above instructions.
Note: If you left Leidos (formerly SAIC) prior to 2003, please email hrcs@leidos.com or phone 1-855-5LE-IDOS (855-553-4367) and select #3.

Outside Firms Requesting Verification
If you are an outside firm verifying someone's employment and/or income at Leidos (formerly SAIC), you will need: 

Employee's Social Security number
Leidos (formerly SAIC) employer code: 12275
Salary key provided by the employee (only needed if you are verifying salary)

To complete verification, call 1-800-367-5690 or go to  The Work Number® and select the "Enter Verifier Section" link. 

Social Service Agencies Requesting Verification
If you are a social service agency verifying someone's employment and/or income at Leidos (formerly SAIC), you will need: 

Registered fax number of your social services agency
Leidos (formerly SAIC) employer code: 12275
Employee’s Social Security number

To complete verification, call 1-800-367-5690 or go to The Work Number® and select the “Enter Social Service Section” link.

Need additional help?
If you need assistance, or you left Leidos (formerly SAIC) prior to 2003, contact:
Email: hrcs@leidos.com
Phone: 1-855-5LE-IDOS (855-553-4367), option #3
Hours: Monday - Friday 8 a.m. to 8 p.m. ET 



Request Investor Information
If you have a question or would like to receive more information, visit the Investors Contact Form and section of our site.



